                 class="text-zinc-300 hover:text-ember transition-colors">Sankar Subbayya</a>
              for the
              <a href="https://lablab.ai"
                 class="text-zinc-300 hover:text-ember transition-colors">Transforming Enterprise Through AI</a>
              hackathon · May 2026
            </span>
